<h1><i class="fa fa-search"></i>Searching Messages</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/sharing-messages"><i class="fa fa-comment"></i>Sharing Messages</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-search"></i>Searching Messages</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>Sometimes it's handy to be able to search your messages to find just the right one.  <%= application.name %> allows a variety of searching options. </p> 

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-search"></i>The Search Menu</h2>
			<p>Searching messages is done by mousing over the "Search" menu on the header bar.  When you select a search menu item, a search box of the selected type will appear in the header bar. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="dropdown menu" src="images/help/sharing-messages/searching-messages/search-menu@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search Menu</div>
			</div>		
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>Search by Message</h2>
			<p>The most commonly used search is to be able to search your messages by the message content. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-messages/searching-messages/search-by-message@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Message</div>
			</div>	
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>Search by Date</h2>
			<p>We can also search by date to find messages posted before or after a certain date, on a particular date. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-messages/searching-messages/search-by-date-before@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Date Before</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-messages/searching-messages/search-by-date-equals@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Date Equals</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-messages/searching-messages/search-by-date-after@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Date After</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>